Association.

00:14:32.860 --> 00:14:34.840
And our panel
session topic today

00:14:34.840 --> 00:14:37.594
is Functions and Dysfunctions
of the Affordable Care Act.

00:14:37.594 --> 00:14:39.010
Conveniently that's
basically what

00:14:39.010 --> 00:14:40.660
I've spent the better
part of the last six years

00:14:40.660 --> 00:14:42.212
studying, along
with my colleagues

00:14:42.212 --> 00:14:44.420
at the Harvard School of
